Whereas according to the POSSUM (Pictures of Standard
			 Syndromes and Undiagnosed Malformations) database, there are more than 600
			 serious diseases and conditions that cause growth failure;

Whereas according to the MAGIC Foundation for Children’s
			 Growth, 48 percent of children in the United States evaluated with the two most
			 common causes of growth failure were undiagnosed;
